## ğŸ—ï¸ New Architecture: Hexagonal (Ports & Adapters)

```
pytaskai/
â”œâ”€â”€ domain/               # ğŸ”µ CORE - Pure business logic
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ entities/         # Task, SubTask business entities  
